	quest.059D97100159C0F5.quest_desc: [
		"&fPause your current series and enter &dFreeroam Mode&f.  "
		"In this mode, &ayour Pokémon can freely reach Level 100&f, with no level cap restrictions.  "
		""
		"&cImportant:&f Freeroam temporarily suspends your current series  "
		"progression. While in Freeroam, you will not advance in any storyline or unlock new milestones.  "
		""
		"You can return to your previous series at any time by:  "
		"&8• &fClicking the dedicated button in the FTB Quests menu of each region.  "
		"&8• &fOr spawning a new Trainer Association NPC to &eselect another series&f and resume where you left off.  "
		""
		"This option is perfect for players who want to explore, train, and catch Pokémon without being limited by level caps, while still keeping the option to return to structured progression."
	]
	quest.059D97100159C0F5.quest_subtitle: "&bNo Level Cap"
	quest.059D97100159C0F5.title: "&dFreeroam Mode"
