	quest.43B32C639F4B3200.quest_desc: [
		"- The &6Steam Engine&r is a block that provides &6Rotational Force&r. It has the highest &6Stress (SU) capacity&r of all the survival-mode power-generating blocks. It converts the pressure caused by heating Water in a &6Fluid Tank&r into &6Rotational Force&r, allowing for large scale item production and multiple contraptions."
		""
		"- &6Level 9 Steam Engines&r are incredibly &6super efficient&r."
		""
