	quest.4B7BEAA7727A9985.title: "Rising Star of Kanto"
	quest.4BB9C36BCFC7E9C6.title: "Smart Filtering"
	quest.4BC7D64DB4ACB7A5.quest_desc: ["A Blaze Burner is a heating component required for certain Mixing recipes."]
	quest.4C07FF85FB34BEAC.quest_subtitle: "This is the perfect gadget for controlling what speed your rotational force is at."
	quest.4C07FF85FB34BEAC.title: "Craft&6 Rotation Speed Controller"
	quest.4C1972B939200EEC.quest_desc: ["A good coffee and here we go again"]
	quest.4C3442628AC11914.quest_desc: [
		"Super Glue holds structures in contraptions together, lime Slimeballs."
		""
		"The main difference between Super Glue and Slimeballs is that Super Glue does not need to use the wooden face of a Linear Chassis to adhere blocks to each other"
	]
	quest.4C43A8015A7E31E1.quest_desc: ["The Pokémon of Galar are distinguished by their diversity: sometimes rustic, sometimes refined. A subtle blend of traditions and evolutions. Their variety of types and behaviors reflect a fascinating complexity. Continue your collection and explore this richness."]
	quest.4C43A8015A7E31E1.title: "Obtain 60 different Pokémon from Generation 8's Pokédex"
	quest.4CA3D6B7B6F566BB.quest_desc: ["The Rolling Mill is used to craft Wires and Rods"]
	quest.4CB8E96CECC63D64.quest_desc: ["As you progress, you approach the mythology of Sinnoh. The Pokémon here seem to be shaped by the cosmos itself. Continue your quest, as the knowledge you gather is invaluable."]
	quest.4CB8E96CECC63D64.title: "Obtain 80 different Pokémon from Generation 4's Pokédex"
	quest.4D9B4F317758E44F.quest_desc: ["Train Tracks are special blocks used to support Trains."]
	quest.4DAB8C40EDBFB070.quest_desc: ["Zekrom, Reshiram, Kyurem… Yin, Yang, and the Void. This is not just a legend. Their influence shapes the entire region and its creatures."]
	quest.4DAB8C40EDBFB070.title: "Obtain 100 different Pokémon from Generation 5's Pokédex"
	quest.4E1B2444D61438D6.title: "&fA Wild &dZeraora &fAppeared!"
	quest.4E4D999C8145C662.quest_desc: ["Engineer's goggles are a wearable item that allow the user to see more details about placed machines"]
	quest.4E609BA887E082A1.quest_desc: [
		"&n&fUsage"
		""
		"&fMulch can be used on a Berry Tree one at a time. It can be removed by interacting with the tree with a shovel, or destroying the tree."
		""
		"&f&nMulch Types"
		""
		"&fA Mulch is an item that is used to craft a variety of different Mulches. It is the fundamental component in creating Mulch used in applying modifiers to berry trees, as well as mutating Revival Herbs. "
	]
	quest.4E609BA887E082A1.title: "Mulch?"
	quest.4E760EF79FA2BCDE.quest_desc: ["Farming will become even more important in Cobblemon. Berries, Apricorns, and medicine all require you to till the fields. "]
	quest.4E87EABAC8A266E7.quest_desc: [
		"While attached to a contraption, the Mechanical Plough will break non-collidable blocks in contact with (ex: Snow Layers)."
		"The Mechanical Plough will also move entities and till soil blocks"
	]
