	quest.4FA1EFB03CA08432.quest_desc: ["When the rotation is reversed, the &6piston&r will retract. The end must be made sticky with a &aSlimeball&r to bring the pushed blocks back with it."]
	quest.4FA1EFB03CA08432.quest_subtitle: "The &cMechanical Piston&r is a piston that can push &aContraptions&r when powered with &eRotational Power&r. To extend, the Piston must have &dPiston Extension Poles&r at the end as well as &eRotational power&r. The maximum extension pole length is &964 blocks&r."
	quest.4FA1EFB03CA08432.title: "Craft a Mechanical Piston"
	quest.4FAEFA9E5BC26DB0.quest_desc: [""]
	quest.4FAEFA9E5BC26DB0.quest_subtitle: "&6Using pairs of Cogwheel and Large Cogwheels, rotational speed can be easily doubled or halved. A Large Cogwheel can also be connected to a Rotation Speed Controller, to adjust speed more precisely.&r"
	quest.4FAEFA9E5BC26DB0.title: "Craft &cLarge Cogwheels"
	quest.4FB43D8DE2D6FC32.quest_desc: ["Sinnoh is known for its evolutionary forms from other regions. Many Pokémon evolve in unique ways here. By capturing 40 species, you’ll begin to understand how the Sinnoh environment shapes evolution."]
	quest.4FB43D8DE2D6FC32.title: "Obtain 40 different Pokémon from Generation 4's Pokédex"
