		"&6&l🏆 Paldea Trainer Progression"
		""
		"&fPaldea’s battle path is not yet available in Cobblemon Realms, but it will come in a future update!"
		""
		"&c⚠ No Trainer Series Available Yet:&r  "
		"&7Currently, no Gym Leaders or Trainer series have been implemented for Paldea. Stay tuned for future updates as we expand the adventure!"
		""
		"&9🎯 In the meantime:&r  "
		"&rWe recommend selecting a Trainer path from another region or generation. You can switch at any time by exchanging a &6Relic Coin&r."
		""
		"&6Thank you for your patience, Trainer. Great things await in Paldea!"
	]
