	quest.54600BAD1C7BC846.quest_desc: ["The Pokémon of Johto are discreet but rich in history. Some are tied to ancient traditions, while others represent evolutionary forms that first appeared here. Start by capturing 20 of them. Even in this altered world, their peaceful and balanced nature remains intact."]
	quest.54600BAD1C7BC846.title: "Obtain 20 different Pokémon from Generation 2's Pokédex"
	quest.551D23A6865FBEEB.quest_desc: ["The Pokémon of Alola are unique, often influenced by the tropical climate and biodiversity that thrives there. Even outside this region, their forms and behaviors will immerse you in the soul of this archipelago. Start by capturing 20 Alola Pokémon and observe how their unique environment influences their evolution."]
	quest.551D23A6865FBEEB.title: "Obtain 20 different Pokémon from Generation 7's Pokédex"
