		"&e&lTrainer Tips:&r&r\\n- Hit \"&eG&r\" to open your party summary and select a starter! \\n- Certain Pokémon appear only in specific biomes or during specific times.\\n- Utilize the new &cpokedex&r to discover more about Pokémon spawns.\\n- Explore additional Cobblemon quests across the chapters on the left!"
	]
