	quest.5BBF89A95474E8AC.quest_desc: [
		"&6⚠ Spawn NPC shops are now the recommended way to buy most items across Cobblemon Realms."
		""
		"&r&f🛒 This legacy Quest Shop will remain available as a convenience feature while the new spawn market continues to expand with additional NPC merchants and categories."
		""
		"&6📈 Prices in this Quest Shop are intentionally 25% to 50% higher than the prices available at the Spawn shops."
		""
		"&r&f💰 You can earn Realms Coins through quests, activities across the world."
		""
		"&7More shop categories and specialized NPC vendors will gradually replace this system in future updates."
