	quest.66B6F883577AF478.quest_desc: ["In Hoenn, new evolutionary concepts emerged: advanced dual typings, weather-related abilities, and even Mega Evolution. These Pokémon reshaped our understanding of life. By capturing 60 of them, you embark on a journey through modern evolution."]
