	quest.67C409C0CA86CF1C.quest_desc: [
		"&e&lCobblemon Realms Tour:&r"
		""
		"* Your Pokémon cannot exceed the current level cap shown on your &fTrainer Card&r."
		"* Once a Pokémon reaches this cap, it will stop gaining experience until you progress further."
		"* Gym Leaders from the &6Cobblemon Realms World Tour&r will refuse to battle you if your team exceeds the current cap."
		"* Defeating major Gym Leaders increases your level cap and unlocks access to stronger regions."
		"* Track your progression using your &fTrainer Card&r, badges, and quests."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		""
		"&e&lGym World Tour:&r"
		""
		"* The &6Cobblemon Realms World Tour&r is a massive challenge spanning multiple Pokémon regions."
		"* Your journey begins in &fKanto&r and progressively leads through Johto, Hoenn, Sinnoh, Unova, Kalos, Galar, and Paldea."
		"* Each region contains increasingly difficult Gym Leaders, stronger Pokémon teams, and higher level caps."
		"* Some late-game Gym Leaders use fully optimized teams and advanced battle strategies."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		""
		"&e&lFinding Gym Leaders:&r"
		""
		"* Gym Leaders are located inside massive custom arenas scattered across the world."
		"* Each arena represents a specific Pokémon type and contains a dedicated battle dimension."
		"* Entering an arena will teleport you into the correct Gym challenge."
		"* Your current progression determines which Gym Leader appears next."
		"* Some arenas may require exploration, biome progression, or previous badges before access."
		"  {image:cobblemonrealmss:textures/ftbquests/logos/gymitem.png width:200 height:110 align:center fit:true}"
		"{@pagebreak}"
		""
		"&e&lBadges and Progression:&r"
		""
		"* Defeating a Gym Leader rewards a unique &fBadge&r stored inside your &fBadge Box&r."
		"* Badges permanently track your progression across all regions."
		"* Some future content, dimensions, systems, and challenges may require specific badges."
		"* Your Badge Box becomes a complete record of your World Tour journey."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		""
		"&e&lCobblemon Realms Features:&r"
		""
		"* Gym progression is fully integrated into the &6Cobblemon Realms Tour&r system."
		"* Quests display all Gym Leaders, unlocked regions, and progression rewards."
		"* Your Trainer Card automatically updates your current level cap and progression."
		"* Special rewards, currencies, cosmetics, and endgame content unlock as you progress further into the World Tour."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		""
		"&e&lTips:&r"
		""
		"* Build multiple Pokémon teams to avoid hitting the level cap too quickly."
		"* Prepare type coverage before entering a new Gym arena."
		"* Some Gym Leaders use competitive strategies, held items, and difficult battle combinations."
		"* Explore the world carefully to discover hidden arenas, rare Pokémon, and progression secrets."
		"{@pagebreak}"
		""
		"&e&lMore Information:&r"
		"For full details about the &fCobblemon Realms World Tour&r system, progression, and future updates:"
		""
		"{\"text\":\"Cobblemon Realms Wiki\",\"color\":\"blue\",\"underlined\":true,\"clickEvent\":{\"action\":\"open_url\",\"value\":\"https://gitbook.io/\"}}"
	]
