	quest.6DA4CAC4C91E0A81.quest_desc: [
		"&fYou’ve caught strong Pokémon, but did you know some can be ridden? With &bCobblemon: Ride On!&r, you can mount your Pokémon and travel the world faster than ever! Learn how to ride, dismount, and control your Pokémon like a pro!"
		"\\n\\n&6🏇 How to Ride Pokémon:&r"
		"&7- Right-click a &arideable Pokémon &7to mount it."
		"&7Use &eWASD &7to move and &eSpace &7to jump (if your Pokémon can)."
		"&9Flying Pokémon: &7Hold &eSpace &7to ascend and &eShift &7to descend."
		"&3Water Pokémon: &7Glide smoothly over water like a true aquatic master!"
		"\\n\\n&c❗ How to Dismount:&r"
		"&7- Press &eLeft Shift &7to safely get off your Pokémon."
		"&4⚠ Warning! &7Make sure you’re not in mid-air when dismounting!"
		"\\n\\n🏆 &aTime to saddle up and explore the world like never before!"
	]
	quest.6DA4CAC4C91E0A81.quest_subtitle: "Master the art of Pokémon riding!"
	quest.6DA4CAC4C91E0A81.title: "Ride Like a Champion!"
	quest.6DB08B23006A0422.quest_desc: ["Many Johto species thrive in tranquil environments: forests, lakes, secluded caves. These Pokémon often live in harmony with nature. By capturing 40 of them, you’ll begin to grasp this deep connection. Observe their behavior: their goal is not conflict, but balance."]
	quest.6DB08B23006A0422.title: "Obtain 40 different Pokémon from Generation 2's Pokédex"
	quest.6DD38045E00D1FC3.quest_desc: ["Want to trash specific items? Dont want your storage cluttered? The open crate drops any item that goes into it on the ground. Drop it into a pool of lava and that pesky trash is no more!"]
	quest.6DD38045E00D1FC3.quest_subtitle: "Garbage Can"
	quest.6DD8E4EEE9DBBF94.quest_desc: ["Some trainers strive to be the best when it comes to battle, and raise only the strongest pokemon. We call them \"Ace\" "]
