	quest.7CF3A317B503AD7C.quest_desc: ["The Portable Fluid Interface is the fluid version of the Portable Storage Interface. It is used to insert or extract from the fluid inventory of a Contraption."]
	quest.7D10898F4947456E.quest_desc: ["Mega Evolution is a temporary &ctransformation&r that greatly enhances a Pokémon's &eStats&r and, in some cases, changes its &bType or Ability&r."]
	quest.7D3D82498C3B327F.quest_desc: [""]
	quest.7D3D82498C3B327F.quest_subtitle: "Copper is Create's block of choice for fluid applications.Just like Andesite casing, you can right click or deploy a copper ingot onto any stripped wood."
